OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor is being
OL,7,Finvestigated by police for sexual
OL,8,Foffences.
OL,10,FThe details emerged as police gave an
OL,11,Fupdate on their criminal investigation
OL,12,Finto misconduct in public office
OL,13,Finvolving the King's younger brother.
OL,15,FThe former prince was sensationally
OL,16,Farrested in February, on his birthday,
OL,17,Fand questioned for 12 hours in a
OL,18,Fpolice station.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FHe was taken into custody in Norfolk
OL,7,Fafter detectives had surprised him at
OL,8,Fbreakfast time and made the arrest on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of the offence of misconduct
OL,10,Fin public office.
OL,12,FIt followed weeks of revelations about
OL,13,FAndrew's friendship with the convicted
OL,14,Fsex offender Jeffrey Epstein, with
OL,15,Fwhom he was alleged to have shared
OL,16,Fsensitive information, while in post
OL,17,Fas trade envoy between 2001 and 2011.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
