OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FMisconduct in public office, an
OL,7,Foffence which carries a maximum
OL,8,Fpunishment of life in prison, is not
OL,9,Flimited to fraud or financial gain.
OL,11,FThe offence concerns serious wilful
OL,12,Fabuse or neglect of the power or
OL,13,Fresponsibilities of the public office
OL,14,Fheld.
OL,16,FThe Crown Prosecution Service clearly
OL,17,Fstates that "the offence can take a
OL,18,Fwide range of forms" and that includes
OL,19,Fcases "involving abuse of position for
OL,20,Fa sexual purpose".
OL,26,@zD@TO]|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
