OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FITV News understands that the Andrew
OL,7,Finvestigation does fall into this
OL,8,Fcategory.
OL,10,FSince Mr Mountabatten-Windsor was
OL,11,F"released under investigation", there
OL,12,Fhave been no developments in the case,
OL,13,Falthough police did carry out
OL,14,Fextensive searches of his home on the
OL,15,FSandringham estate and his former
OL,16,Fhome, Royal Lodge, on the Windsor
OL,17,FEstate.
OL,19,FMaterial recovered during those
OL,20,Fsearches is still being worked through.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
