CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FThames Valley Police Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable Oliver Wright said: "Our
OL,8,Fteam of very experienced detectives
OL,9,Fare working meticulously through a
OL,10,Fsignificant amount of information that
OL,11,Fhas come in from the public and other
OL,12,Fsources. We are committed to
OL,13,Fconducting a thorough investigation
OL,14,Finto all reasonable lines of enquiry,
OL,15,Fwherever they may lead."
OL,17,FThose in charge of this investigation
OL,18,Fhave also confirmed they are in touch
OL,19,Fwith the US Department of Justice,
OL,20,Fwhich released three million Epstein
OL,21,Ffiles earlier this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
