PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FBut they declined to reveal what, if
OL,7,Fany, new information they had been
OL,8,Fgiven from Washington.
OL,10,FOfficers have also been speaking to "a
OL,11,Fnumber of witnesses", but their
OL,12,Fidentities have not been revealed.
OL,14,FAll the while, the force has been
OL,15,Fliaising with the Crown Prosecution
OL,16,FService as they assess all the
OL,17,Finformation in what they call a
OL,18,F"serious, complex" case.
OL,26,@sD@TO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
