OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Oliver
OL,7,FWright said: "Our misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice investigation is continuing.
OL,9,FMisconduct in public office is a crime
OL,10,Fthat can take different forms, making
OL,11,Fthis a complex investigation."
OL,13,FPrince Andrew has always strenuously
OL,14,Fdenied any wrongdoing in relation to
OL,15,Fall the allegations made against him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
