OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,FOn the day of his arrest in February,
OL,7,Fthe King released a written statement
OL,8,Fwhich said: "I have learned with the
OL,9,Fdeepest concern the news about Andrew
OL,10,FMountbatten-Windsor and suspicion of
OL,11,Fmisconduct in public office. What now
OL,12,Ffollows is the full, fair and proper
OL,13,Fprocess by which this issue is
OL,14,Finvestigated in the appropriate manner
OL,15,Fand by the appropriate authorities. In
OL,16,Fthis, as I have said before, they have
OL,17,Four full and wholehearted support and
OL,18,Fco-operation.
OL,20,F"Let me state clearly: the law must
OL,21,Ftake its course.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
