PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1779620575
OL,3,CAndrew police investigation examining
OL,4,Csexual offence claims
OL,6,F"As this process continues, it would
OL,7,Fnot be right for me to comment further
OL,8,Fon this matter. Meanwhile, my family
OL,9,Fand I will continue in our duty and
OL,10,Fservice to you all."
OL,12,FIt is not thought that Buckingham
OL,13,FPalace will respond to this latest
OL,14,Fupdate.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
